  final String score1 =
      'Score 1: An essay at this level largely accomplishes all of the following: • Serious disorganization or underdevelopment • Little or no detail, or irrelevant specifics, or questionable responsiveness to the task • Serious and frequent errors in sentence structure or usage ';

